snippet.title: King of Retail - Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Welcome to the launch of King of Retail! The store is your kingdom! Expand your humble boutique into a thriving business: hire the right staff, decorate your displays, and lure in customers. Even your wildest ideas can turn a profit. Why not start a business that sells only white T-shirts and ketchup? PCs and beans? Your rule, your rules!

King of Retail is available on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/968250/King_of_Retail/
